extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to the #[em Borderlands 2] database. Sort weapons from the  video game by manufacturer, type, element, and rarity.

  h2 Inventory 

  if error 
    p Error getting inventory from database 
  else 
    p The inventory has the following record counts: 

    ul.list 
      li #[strong Weapons:] #{data.weaponCount} 
      li #[strong Manufacturers:] #{data.manufacturerCount} 
      li #[strong Types:] #{data.typeCount}  
      li #[strong Elements:] #{data.elementCount}  
      li #[strong Rarities:] #{data.rarityCount} 
